# Workspace configuration

## `abd-config.json` (required)



| Key | Required | Meaning |

| --- | --- | --- |

| **`active_skill_workspace`** | **Yes** | Root of the **skill workspace** (the project/solution where this skill runs). **Mandatory** — the skill install folder only holds this pointer; it does not hold the customer project. Prefer an absolute path. Relative paths resolve from **`skill_path`** (the skill install directory). |

| **`known_skill_workspaces`** | No | Optional list of other workspace roots this skill has used so you can switch without scattering paths. |



**Deprecated:** `solution_workspace`, `skill_space_path` — same role; migrate to **`active_skill_workspace`**.



See **`abd-skill-builder`** `content/parts/library/workspace-config.md` (in the skills repo) for **`skill_path`** vs **`skill_workspace`**.

